Troubleshooting Tips
Zeek not capturing traffic:

Verify network interface name in node.cfg
Check interface is up: ip link show
Ensure sufficient permissions: sudo zeekctl
Review Zeek logs: tail /opt/zeek/logs/current/reporter.log
No beacons detected:

Verify sufficient traffic volume (run traffic generator longer)
Lower detection thresholds (increase max_cv parameter)
Check log parsing: python3 zeek_parser.py
Ensure timestamps are correctly parsed
Python import errors:

Activate virtual environment: source venv/bin/activate
Reinstall dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt
Check Python version: python3 --version (requires 3.7+)
